Q) what is the diffence between null and undefined?
Ans)

null -- absence of value

undefined -- absence of datatype

Q)how to identify the datatype of a variable in JS?

Ans)by using typeof keyword.

Q)how to create a string variable in JS?
ans) by using the single or double quotes.

